jalse.entities

Interface EntityProxyFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultEntityProxyFactory

    public interface EntityProxyFactory
    This defines a factory for creating Entity proxies. Making a proxy of an Entity subclass allows the InvocationHandler to translate the method calls into Entity methods. This makes the subclasses more customisable for specific problems.
    See Also:
    DefaultEntityProxyFactory, EntityFunctionResolver
